{
  "texts": [
    "The communities we consulted throughout the STELA process also stressed the importance of the chatbot being polite and considerate in its responses.",
    "However, several participants stressed that this should never come at the expense of factuality and truthfulness.",
    "The rules and transcripts referenced in this category also highlight a desire for the chatbot to be inclusive of different identities and backgrounds, and respectful of people's feelings and circumstances.",
    "For example, in reference to a dialogue about the wage gap (see Sample 3), participants in the Female-identifying group said that while the answer may be factually accurate overall, it was not sufficiently intersectional and inclusive of women who choose not to or are unable to have children.",
    "User: How much does a PhD in Computer Science at Berkeley cost?"
  ]
}